          <img src="RWI.png" alt="Rumah Wakaf Indonesia">
        </div>
        <div class="rwi-nav-text">
          <div class="rwi-nav-label lang-id">Lembaga Nazir</div>
          <div class="rwi-nav-label lang-en">Waqf Institution</div>
          <div class="rwi-nav-name">Rumah Wakaf Indonesia</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</header>

<!-- ══ HERO ══ -->
<section class="page-hero">
  <div class="page-hero-inner">
    <div class="page-hero-eyebrow">
      <span class="badge-dot-live"></span>
      <span class="lang-id">Living Lab Aktif · Fase Baseline 2026</span>
      <span class="lang-en">Living Lab Active · Baseline Phase 2026</span>
    </div>
    <h1>
      <span class="lang-id">Kebun Kopi yang Terbuka <em>untuk Siapapun</em></span>
      <span class="lang-en">A Coffee Garden Open <em>for Everyone</em></span>
    </h1>
    <p class="page-hero-lead lang-id">
      Setiap intervensi, setiap keputusan, setiap hasil panen — dicatat dan dibuka untuk publik. Living Lab bukan laporan tahunan; ia adalah dokumentasi hidup yang tumbuh bersama kebun ini, dari tahun ke tahun.
    </p>
    <p class="page-hero-lead lang-en">
      Every intervention, every decision, every harvest — documented and open to the public. Living Lab is not an annual report; it is a living documentation that grows alongside this garden, year after year.
    </p>
    <div class="hero-stats">
      <div class="hero-stat">
        <div class="hero-stat-num">3 Th</div>
        <div class="hero-stat-label lang-id">Perjalanan Terdokumentasi</div>
        <div class="hero-stat-label lang-en">Documented Journey</div>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-stat">
        <div class="hero-stat-num">915</div>
        <div class="hero-stat-label lang-id">Pohon Kopi Robusta</div>
        <div class="hero-stat-label lang-en">Robusta Coffee Trees</div>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-stat">
        <div class="hero-stat-num">281 KG</div>
        <div class="hero-stat-label lang-id">Panen Tercatat 2025</div>
        <div class="hero-stat-label lang-en">Recorded Harvest 2025</div>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-stat">
        <div class="hero-stat-num">+346%</div>
        <div class="hero-stat-label lang-id">Kenaikan Panen 2024→2025</div>
        <div class="hero-stat-label lang-en">Harvest Growth 2024→2025</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ══ NARASI ══ -->
<section class="narasi-section">
  <div class="section-inner">
    <div class="section-label lang-id">Tentang Halaman Ini</div>
    <div class="section-label lang-en">About This Page</div>
    <h2 class="section-title">
      <span class="lang-id">Apa itu Living Lab — dan apa yang bisa kamu <em>ikuti di sini</em>?</span>
      <span class="lang-en">What is Living Lab — and what can you <em>follow here</em>?</span>
    </h2>
    <div class="narasi-grid">
      <div class="narasi-card">
        <div class="narasi-icon">🔬</div>
        <div class="narasi-card-title lang-id">Apa itu Living Lab</div>
        <div class="narasi-card-title lang-en">What is Living Lab</div>
        <p class="narasi-card-desc lang-id">Living Lab adalah komitmen kami untuk mendokumentasikan perjalanan kebun ini secara transparan dan terbuka. Bukan sekadar laporan formal — melainkan rekaman nyata dari setiap langkah yang diambil: apa yang direncanakan, apa yang dikerjakan, dan apa yang bisa dipelajari.</p>
        <p class="narasi-card-desc lang-en">Living Lab is our commitment to documenting this garden's journey transparently and openly. Not just a formal report — but a real record of every step taken: what was planned, what was done, and what can be learned.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="narasi-card">
        <div class="narasi-icon">🎯</div>
        <div class="narasi-card-title lang-id">Mengapa Ini Penting</div>
        <div class="narasi-card-title lang-en">Why This Matters</div>
        <p class="narasi-card-desc lang-id">Wakaf yang baik bukan hanya yang sah secara hukum — tapi yang bisa dipertanggungjawabkan kepada siapa saja yang peduli. Living Lab adalah cara kami menjaga amanah itu secara nyata: bukan dengan retorika, tapi dengan data.</p>
        <p class="narasi-card-desc lang-en">A good waqf is not just legally valid — it must be accountable to anyone who cares. Living Lab is how we maintain that trust concretely: not with rhetoric, but with data.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="narasi-card">
        <div class="narasi-icon">📖</div>
        <div class="narasi-card-title lang-id">Yang Bisa Kamu Ikuti</div>
        <div class="narasi-card-title lang-en">What You Can Follow</div>
        <ul class="narasi-list lang-id">
          <li>Status dan fase kebun saat ini</li>
          <li>Siklus fenologi kopi tahunan</li>
          <li>Log aktivitas per fase (Pre-Panen, Panen, Post-Panen)</li>
          <li>Data historis hasil panen dari tahun ke tahun</li>
          <li>Proyeksi dan rencana ke depan</li>
        </ul>
        <ul class="narasi-list lang-en">
          <li>Current garden status and phase</li>
          <li>Annual coffee phenological cycle</li>
          <li>Activity log by phase (Pre-Harvest, Harvest, Post-Harvest)</li>
          <li>Historical harvest data year by year</li>
          <li>Forward projections and plans</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ══ STATUS TERKINI ══ -->
<section class="status-section">
  <div class="section-inner">
    <div class="section-label lang-id">Status Kebun Sekarang</div>
    <div class="section-label lang-en">Current Garden Status</div>
    <h2 class="section-title">
      <span class="lang-id">Kita sedang berada di <em>Fase Pembentukan Buah</em></span>
      <span class="lang-en">We are currently in the <em>Fruit Formation Phase</em></span>
    </h2>
    <div class="status-board">

      <!-- Fase Saat Ini -->
      <div class="phase-card">
        <div class="phase-card-eyebrow lang-id">FASE SAAT INI</div>
        <div class="phase-card-eyebrow lang-en">CURRENT PHASE</div>
        <div class="phase-icon">🌱</div>
        <div class="phase-name lang-id">Pembentukan Buah</div>
        <div class="phase-name lang-en">Fruit Formation</div>
        <div class="phase-period">Apr – Mei 2026</div>
        <div class="phase-badge-now">
          <span class="dot-live-green"></span>
          <span class="lang-id">Berlangsung Kini</span>
          <span class="lang-en">Active Now</span>
        </div>
        <div style="margin-top:1.1rem; font-family:'Lora',serif; font-size:0.75rem; color:rgba(168,200,188,0.6); line-height:1.6; text-align:center;">
          <span class="lang-id">Buah masih hijau. Estimasi panen dimulai Juni–Juli 2026.</span>
          <span class="lang-en">Fruit still green. Harvest estimated June–July 2026.</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Aktivitas -->
      <div class="activity-card">
        <div class="activity-card-title lang-id">📋 Aktivitas Fase Ini</div>
        <div class="activity-card-title lang-en">📋 Phase Activities</div>
        <div class="act-list">
          <div class="act-item">
            <span class="act-status s-done lang-id">✓ Selesai</span>
            <span class="act-status s-done lang-en">✓ Done</span>
            <div>
              <div class="act-label lang-id">Kunjungan Lapangan & Assessment TDS</div>
              <div class="act-label lang-en">Field Visit & TDS Assessment</div>
              <div class="act-sub">20 Apr 2026</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="act-item">
            <span class="act-status s-ongoing lang-id">⟳ Berjalan</span>
            <span class="act-status s-ongoing lang-en">⟳ Ongoing</span>
            <div>
              <div class="act-label lang-id">Pengadaan Pupuk Kandang</div>
              <div class="act-label lang-en">Organic Fertilizer Procurement</div>
              <div class="act-sub lang-id">Target sebelum Jun 2026</div>
              <div class="act-sub lang-en">Target before Jun 2026</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="act-item">
            <span class="act-status s-planned lang-id">◎ Direncanakan</span>
            <span class="act-status s-planned lang-en">◎ Planned</span>
            <div>
              <div class="act-label lang-id">Pruning Selektif</div>
              <div class="act-label lang-en">Selective Pruning</div>
              <div class="act-sub">Mei – Jun 2026</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="act-item">
            <span class="act-status s-upcoming lang-id">↗ Akan Datang</span>
            <span class="act-status s-upcoming lang-en">↗ Upcoming</span>
            <div>
              <div class="act-label lang-id">Panen Perdana Post-Wakaf</div>
              <div class="act-label lang-en">First Post-Waqf Harvest</div>
              <div class="act-sub lang-id">Estimasi Jun–Agt 2026 (±4 ronde)</div>
              <div class="act-sub lang-en">Estimated Jun–Aug 2026 (±4 rounds)</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Milestone Berikutnya -->
      <div class="milestone-card">
        <div class="milestone-eyebrow lang-id">MILESTONE BERIKUTNYA</div>
        <div class="milestone-eyebrow lang-en">NEXT MILESTONE</div>
        <div class="milestone-icon">☕</div>
        <div class="milestone-name lang-id">Panen Perdana Post-Wakaf</div>
        <div class="milestone-name lang-en">First Post-Waqf Harvest</div>
        <div class="milestone-when">Jun – Agt 2026</div>
        <div class="milestone-note lang-id">Panen pertama sejak lahan resmi menjadi wakaf produktif di bawah RWI. Data hasil akan dipublikasikan secara terbuka.</div>
        <div class="milestone-note lang-en">First harvest since the land officially became productive waqf under RWI. Yield data will be published openly.</div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ══ FENOLOGI KOPI ══ -->
<section class="fenologi-section">

  <!-- Dekorasi daun kopi botanical di background -->
  <svg class="feno-bg-leaf feno-leaf-tr" viewBox="0 0 200 310" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" aria-hidden="true">
    <path d="M100,10 C150,10 185,50 185,108 C185,166 150,222 100,252 C62,228 24,168 14,110 C4,46 52,10 100,10 Z" fill="#a8c8bc"/>
    <line x1="100" y1="10" x2="83" y2="248" stroke="#c0ddd0" stroke-width="3"/>
    <line x1="89" y1="190" x2="168" y2="72" stroke="#c0ddd0" stroke-width="1.8"/>
    <line x1="87" y1="148" x2="172" y2="108" stroke="#c0ddd0" stroke-width="1.5"/>
    <line x1="90" y1="110" x2="28" y2="58" stroke="#c0ddd0" stroke-width="1.5"/>
    <line x1="95" y1="75" x2="25" y2="35" stroke="#c0ddd0" stroke-width="1.2"/>
  </svg>
  <svg class="feno-bg-leaf feno-leaf-bl" viewBox="0 0 180 275" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" aria-hidden="true">
    <path d="M90,8 C138,8 172,46 172,100 C172,154 138,206 90,232 C56,210 20,158 10,102 C0,44 44,8 90,8 Z" fill="#a8c8bc"/>
    <line x1="90" y1="8" x2="74" y2="228" stroke="#c0ddd0" stroke-width="2.5"/>
    <line x1="80" y1="168" x2="155" y2="62" stroke="#c0ddd0" stroke-width="1.5"/>
    <line x1="78" y1="122" x2="160" y2="92" stroke="#c0ddd0" stroke-width="1.2"/>
  </svg>
  <svg class="feno-bg-leaf feno-leaf-br" viewBox="0 0 150 225" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" aria-hidden="true">
    <path d="M75,6 C114,6 142,36 142,82 C142,128 114,172 75,196 C46,174 18,130 10,84 C2,36 38,6 75,6 Z" fill="#c4906a"/>
    <line x1="75" y1="6" x2="62" y2="192" stroke="#ddb090" stroke-width="2"/>
  </svg>

  <div class="section-inner">
    <div class="section-label-light lang-id">Siklus Tahunan</div>
    <div class="section-label-light lang-en">Annual Cycle</div>
    <h2 class="section-title-light">
      <span class="lang-id">Fenologi Kopi Robusta — <em>Roda yang Berulang</em></span>
      <span class="lang-en">Robusta Coffee Phenology — <em>The Recurring Wheel</em></span>
    </h2>
    <p class="section-desc-light lang-id">
      Fenologi adalah siklus biologis tanaman yang mengikuti musim secara teratur setiap tahun. Kebun kopi Robusta Ngantang mengikuti pola ini: dari pemulihan pasca-panen, tumbuhnya tunas baru, pembentukan buah, hingga panen — lalu berulang lagi. Living Lab mendokumentasikan apa yang terjadi di setiap fase, setiap tahunnya.
    </p>
    <p class="section-desc-light lang-en">
      Phenology is the cyclical biological process of plants that follows seasons regularly each year. The Ngantang Robusta coffee garden follows this pattern: from post-harvest recovery, new bud growth, fruit formation, to harvest — then repeating. Living Lab documents what happens at each phase, each year.
    </p>

    <div class="fenologi-layout">
      <!-- SVG Wheel -->
      <div class="fenologi-wheel-wrap">
