      <!-- Legend -->
      <div>
        <div class="fenologi-legend">
          <div class="legend-item">
            <div class="legend-swatch" style="background:#7a9e96;"></div>
            <div class="legend-content">
              <div class="legend-phase lang-id">Pemulihan & Dormansi</div>
              <div class="legend-phase lang-en">Recovery & Dormancy</div>
              <div class="legend-months lang-id">Jan, Nov, Des</div>
              <div class="legend-months lang-en">Jan, Nov, Dec</div>
              <div class="legend-desc lang-id">Pohon beristirahat setelah panen. Fase penting untuk memulihkan energi tanaman sebelum siklus berikutnya dimulai.</div>
              <div class="legend-desc lang-en">Trees rest after harvest. A critical phase for restoring plant energy before the next cycle begins.</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="legend-item">
            <div class="legend-swatch" style="background:#5a9080;"></div>
            <div class="legend-content">
              <div class="legend-phase lang-id">Pertumbuhan Vegetatif</div>
              <div class="legend-phase lang-en">Vegetative Growth</div>
              <div class="legend-months">Feb – Mar</div>
              <div class="legend-desc lang-id">Tunas baru tumbuh. Daun dan cabang berkembang aktif — fondasi untuk musim berbuah berikutnya.</div>
              <div class="legend-desc lang-en">New buds emerge. Leaves and branches develop actively — the foundation for the next fruiting season.</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="legend-item">
            <div class="legend-swatch" style="background:#7db848;"></div>
            <div class="legend-content">
              <div class="legend-phase lang-id">Pembentukan Buah ← Sekarang</div>
              <div class="legend-phase lang-en">Fruit Formation ← Now</div>
              <div class="legend-months">Apr – Mei</div>
              <div class="legend-desc lang-id">Buah kopi terbentuk dan mulai berkembang. Masa kritis untuk nutrisi dan perlindungan tanaman.</div>
              <div class="legend-desc lang-en">Coffee fruit forms and begins developing. A critical time for plant nutrition and protection.</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="legend-item">
            <div class="legend-swatch" style="background:#c8a840;"></div>
            <div class="legend-content">
              <div class="legend-phase lang-id">Pematangan Buah</div>
              <div class="legend-phase lang-en">Fruit Ripening</div>
              <div class="legend-months">Jun</div>
              <div class="legend-desc lang-id">Buah mulai menguning — tanda panen segera dimulai. Pengawasan intensif dibutuhkan.</div>
              <div class="legend-desc lang-en">Fruit begins to yellow — a sign harvest is about to begin. Intensive monitoring is needed.</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="legend-item">
            <div class="legend-swatch" style="background:#c4906a;"></div>
            <div class="legend-content">
              <div class="legend-phase lang-id">Panen Utama</div>
              <div class="legend-phase lang-en">Main Harvest</div>
              <div class="legend-months">Jul – Agt</div>
              <div class="legend-desc lang-id">Panen dilakukan bertahap dalam 4 ronde. Buah dipetik selektif sesuai tingkat kematangan untuk menjaga kualitas.</div>
              <div class="legend-desc lang-en">Harvest is done in 4 rounds. Cherries are selectively picked by ripeness to maintain quality.</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="legend-item">
            <div class="legend-swatch" style="background:#3d7868;"></div>
            <div class="legend-content">
              <div class="legend-phase lang-id">Post-Panen & Intervensi</div>
              <div class="legend-phase lang-en">Post-Harvest & Intervention</div>
              <div class="legend-months">Sep – Okt</div>
              <div class="legend-desc lang-id">Pruning total, pemulihan tanah, dan intervensi rehabilitasi. Fase ini menentukan produktivitas musim berikutnya.</div>
              <div class="legend-desc lang-en">Full pruning, soil recovery, and rehabilitation interventions. This phase determines the next season's productivity.</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="fenologi-note lang-id">
          Siklus ini berulang setiap tahun — dan Living Lab akan terus mendokumentasikan apa yang terjadi di setiap fasenya. Dalam 5–10 tahun ke depan, halaman ini menjadi rekaman lengkap perjalanan kebun dari nol hingga menjadi aset wakaf yang produktif.
        </div>
        <div class="fenologi-note lang-en">
          This cycle repeats every year — and Living Lab will continue to document what happens at each phase. Over the next 5–10 years, this page becomes a complete record of the garden's journey from zero to a productive waqf asset.
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

