    <p class="section-desc lang-id">Rekaman seluruh aktivitas dan intervensi di kebun, diorganisir berdasarkan tahun dan fase fenologi. Setiap entri mencatat apa yang dilakukan, kapan, dan apa hasilnya.</p>
    <p class="section-desc lang-en">A record of all garden activities and interventions, organized by year and phenological phase. Each entry records what was done, when, and what the outcome was.</p>

