              <div class="act-log-title lang-id">Panen Perdana Terdokumentasi</div>
              <div class="act-log-title lang-en">First Documented Harvest</div>
              <div class="act-log-detail lang-id">Panen pertama yang tercatat secara formal. Menghasilkan sekitar 100 KG green bean — angka awal yang menjadi baseline untuk pertumbuhan ke depan.</div>
              <div class="act-log-detail lang-en">First formally recorded harvest. Yielding approximately 100 KG green bean — an initial figure that became the baseline for future growth.</div>
            </div>
            <div class="act-log-meta"><strong>~100 KG</strong>Green Bean</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="phase-block">
        <div class="phase-block-header">
          <span class="phase-block-icon">🌿</span>
          <span class="phase-block-title lang-id">Post-Panen</span>
          <span class="phase-block-title lang-en">Post-Harvest</span>
          <span class="phase-block-period lang-id">Sep – Des 2024</span>
          <span class="phase-block-period lang-en">Sep – Dec 2024</span>
        </div>
        <div class="act-log-list">
          <div class="act-log-item">
            <span class="act-log-status s-done lang-id">✓ Selesai</span>
            <span class="act-log-status s-done lang-en">✓ Done</span>
            <div class="act-log-body">
              <div class="act-log-title lang-id">Replanting 330 Bibit (tidak berhasil)</div>
              <div class="act-log-title lang-en">Replanting 330 Seedlings (unsuccessful)</div>
              <div class="act-log-detail lang-id">Upaya peremajaan dengan 330 bibit baru. Seluruh bibit tidak bertahan — pelajaran penting: replanting membutuhkan pengawalan intensif dan jadwal yang tepat.</div>
              <div class="act-log-detail lang-en">Rejuvenation attempt with 330 new seedlings. All seedlings did not survive — an important lesson: replanting requires intensive supervision and proper timing.</div>
            </div>
            <div class="act-log-meta"><strong>Okt 2024</strong>Pembelajaran</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- 2025 -->
    <div class="year-content" id="year-2025">
      <div class="year-summary">
        <div class="year-sum-pill lang-id"><strong>281 KG</strong> Green Bean Tercatat</div>
        <div class="year-sum-pill lang-en"><strong>281 KG</strong> Green Bean Recorded</div>
        <div class="year-sum-pill lang-id"><strong>+346%</strong> dari 2024</div>
        <div class="year-sum-pill lang-en"><strong>+346%</strong> from 2024</div>
        <div class="year-sum-pill lang-id">MOU Wakaf: <strong>27 Nov 2025</strong></div>
        <div class="year-sum-pill lang-en">Waqf MOU: <strong>27 Nov 2025</strong></div>
      </div>

      <div class="phase-block">
        <div class="phase-block-header">
