            <div class="act-log-body">
              <div class="act-log-title lang-id">Panen 2025 — Lonjakan Signifikan</div>
              <div class="act-log-title lang-en">2025 Harvest — Significant Surge</div>
              <div class="act-log-detail lang-id">281 KG green bean — kenaikan 346% dari tahun sebelumnya. Produktivitas mencapai 0,31 KG/pohon, mendekati rata-rata nasional 0,4 KG/pohon. Fondasi nyata mulai terbangun.</div>
              <div class="act-log-detail lang-en">281 KG green bean — a 346% increase from the previous year. Productivity reached 0.31 KG/tree, approaching the national average of 0.4 KG/tree. A real foundation is beginning to form.</div>
            </div>
            <div class="act-log-meta"><strong>281 KG</strong>+346%</div>
          </div>
        </div>
