      <div class="phase-block">
        <div class="phase-block-header">
          <span class="phase-block-icon">📜</span>
          <span class="phase-block-title lang-id">Post-Panen & Milestone</span>
          <span class="phase-block-title lang-en">Post-Harvest & Milestone</span>
          <span class="phase-block-period lang-id">Sep – Des 2025</span>
          <span class="phase-block-period lang-en">Sep – Dec 2025</span>
        </div>
        <div class="act-log-list">
          <div class="act-log-item">
            <span class="act-log-status s-done lang-id">✓ Selesai</span>
            <span class="act-log-status s-done lang-en">✓ Done</span>
            <div class="act-log-body">
              <div class="act-log-title lang-id">Penandatanganan MOU Wakaf Produktif</div>
              <div class="act-log-title lang-en">Productive Waqf MOU Signing</div>
              <div class="act-log-detail lang-id">Alhamdulillah — ikrar resmi ditandatangani bersama Rumah Wakaf Indonesia. Perkebunan Kopi & Durian Bonsari resmi menjadi wakaf produktif. Tonggak paling bermakna dalam perjalanan ini.</div>
              <div class="act-log-detail lang-en">Alhamdulillah — the formal pledge was signed with Rumah Wakaf Indonesia. Bonsari Coffee & Durian Farm officially became productive waqf. The most meaningful milestone of this journey.</div>
            </div>
            <div class="act-log-meta"><strong>27 Nov 2025</strong>Milestone</div>
          </div>
        </div>
