    <!-- 2026 -->
    <div class="year-content active" id="year-2026">
      <div class="active-year-banner">
        <div class="active-year-dot"></div>
        <span class="active-year-label lang-id">Tahun Berjalan — 2026</span>
        <span class="active-year-label lang-en">Current Year — 2026</span>
        <span class="active-year-desc lang-id">Rehabilitasi aktif & intervensi Tenaga Ahli sedang berlangsung</span>
        <span class="active-year-desc lang-en">Active rehabilitation & Technical Advisor interventions underway</span>
      </div>
      <div class="year-summary">
        <div class="year-sum-pill lang-id">Fase: <strong>Pembentukan Buah</strong></div>
        <div class="year-sum-pill lang-en">Phase: <strong>Fruit Formation</strong></div>
        <div class="year-sum-pill lang-id">Intervensi Tenaga Ahli: <strong>Jan–Mar</strong></div>
        <div class="year-sum-pill lang-en">Technical Advisor Interventions: <strong>Jan–Mar</strong></div>
        <div class="year-sum-pill lang-id">Tenaga Ahli Kebun: <strong>T.A. Aktif</strong></div>
        <div class="year-sum-pill lang-en">Technical Advisor: <strong>Active</strong></div>
        <div class="year-sum-pill lang-id">Target Panen: <strong>Jun–Agt 2026</strong></div>
        <div class="year-sum-pill lang-en">Harvest Target: <strong>Jun–Aug 2026</strong></div>
      </div>

      <div class="phase-block">
        <div class="phase-block-header">
          <span class="phase-block-icon">🌱</span>
          <span class="phase-block-title lang-id">Pre-Panen</span>
          <span class="phase-block-title lang-en">Pre-Harvest</span>
          <span class="phase-block-period lang-id">Apr – Jun 2026</span>
          <span class="phase-block-period lang-en">Apr – Jun 2026</span>
        </div>
        <div class="act-log-list">
          <div class="act-log-item">
            <span class="act-log-status s-done lang-id">✓ Selesai</span>
            <span class="act-log-status s-done lang-en">✓ Done</span>
            <div class="act-log-body">
              <div class="act-log-title lang-id">Pemupukan Makro & Penyemprotan Nutrisi Awal — Tenaga Ahli</div>
              <div class="act-log-title lang-en">Macro Fertilization & Initial Nutrient Spray — Technical Advisor</div>
              <div class="act-log-detail lang-id">Intervensi teknis pertama di bawah bimbingan Tenaga Ahli. Aplikasi pupuk makro (Karate Plus Boron, Ponska Plus, Fertiphos, NPK Yaramila 16.16.16) dan mikro (MKP, Vita Flex, CNG, MGs, Ultradap, ZnS), serta treatment khusus SNC, NPGP, CN cair & serbuk. Penyemprotan rutin setiap 10 hari — tiap sesi 12 tangki (220 liter).</div>
              <div class="act-log-detail lang-en">First technical intervention under specialist guidance. Applied macro fertilizers (Karate Plus Boron, Ponska Plus, Fertiphos, NPK Yaramila 16.16.16), micro nutrients (MKP, Vita Flex, CNG, MGs, Ultradap, ZnS), and special treatments SNC, NPGP, CN liquid & powder. Routine spray every 10 days — 12 tanks (220 liters) per session.</div>
            </div>
            <div class="act-log-meta"><strong>8 Jan 2026</strong>T.A.</div>
          </div>

          <div class="act-log-item">
            <span class="act-log-status s-done lang-id">✓ Selesai</span>
            <span class="act-log-status s-done lang-en">✓ Done</span>
            <div class="act-log-body">
              <div class="act-log-title lang-id">Penggemburan Tanah + Aplikasi Kompos Ayam (65 Sak)</div>
              <div class="act-log-title lang-en">Soil Aeration + Poultry Compost Application (65 Sacks)</div>
              <div class="act-log-detail lang-id">Penggemburan tanah menggunakan garpu di seluruh area tajuk pohon — memotong sebagian akar serabut untuk memacu pertumbuhan akar baru. Bersamaan dengan tabur 65 sak kompos ayam petelur (3–5 KG/pohon). Kedalaman garpu maksimal 20 cm, posisi menghadap batang. Dilaksanakan selama 3 minggu oleh tim lapangan.</div>
              <div class="act-log-detail lang-en">Soil aeration using forks across the canopy area — partially cutting fibrous roots to stimulate new root growth. Concurrent with distribution of 65 sacks of poultry compost (3–5 KG/tree). Max fork depth 20 cm, facing the trunk. Carried out over 3 weeks by the field team.</div>
            </div>
            <div class="act-log-meta"><strong>31 Jan–20 Feb</strong>2026</div>
          </div>

          <div class="act-log-item">
            <span class="act-log-status s-done lang-id">✓ Selesai</span>
            <span class="act-log-status s-done lang-en">✓ Done</span>
            <div class="act-log-body">
              <div class="act-log-title lang-id">Pemasangan Meter Air PDAM Desa</div>
              <div class="act-log-title lang-en">Village PDAM Water Meter Installation</div>
              <div class="act-log-detail lang-id">Infrastruktur air bersih terpasang di kebun — menggantikan pengambilan air manual dari rumah Wakif menggunakan jerigen. Mendukung operasional penyemprotan rutin 220 liter/sesi secara jauh lebih efisien dan konsisten.</div>
              <div class="act-log-detail lang-en">Clean water infrastructure installed at the garden — replacing manual water transport from the Wakif's house via jerrycans. Enables efficient, consistent routine spraying of 220 liters per session.</div>
            </div>
            <div class="act-log-meta"><strong>7 Mar 2026</strong>Infrastruktur</div>
          </div>

          <div class="act-log-item">
            <span class="act-log-status s-done lang-id">✓ Selesai</span>
            <span class="act-log-status s-done lang-en">✓ Done</span>
            <div class="act-log-body">
              <div class="act-log-title lang-id">Pengocoran Fish Extract Perdana</div>
              <div class="act-log-title lang-en">First Fish Extract Soil Drench Application</div>
              <div class="act-log-detail lang-id">Pengocoran 100 cc fish extract per pohon + 900 cc air = 1 liter/pohon. Fish extract diproduksi mandiri di Wonosalam (1.000 liter; bahan: air kelapa 250L, molase 100L, limbah ikan laut 500 KG, bioactivator 20 KG). Setelah serangkaian intervensi ini, tunas baru dan bunga perdana mulai bermunculan di ujung cabang — tanda rejuvenasi nyata mulai terlihat.</div>
              <div class="act-log-detail lang-en">Application of 100cc fish extract per tree + 900cc water = 1 liter/tree. Fish extract self-produced in Wonosalam (1,000 liters; ingredients: coconut water 250L, molasses 100L, sea fish waste 500 KG, bioactivator 20 KG). After this series of interventions, new buds and first flowers began emerging at branch tips — visible signs of rejuvenation underway.</div>
            </div>
            <div class="act-log-meta"><strong>15 Mar 2026</strong>T.A.</div>
          </div>

          <div class="act-log-item">
            <span class="act-log-status s-done lang-id">✓ Selesai</span>
            <span class="act-log-status s-done lang-en">✓ Done</span>
            <div class="act-log-body">
              <div class="act-log-title lang-id">Kunjungan Lapangan Perdana & Assessment Baseline</div>
              <div class="act-log-title lang-en">First Field Visit & Baseline Assessment</div>
              <div class="act-log-detail lang-id">Bersama Tenaga Ahli Kebun (15+ tahun pengalaman). Sampling TDS tanah di 5 titik — hasil: tanah berpasir dengan defisiensi mineral. Evaluasi kondisi 915 pohon. Proyeksi panen ditetapkan: Juni–Juli 2026, ±4 ronde.</div>
              <div class="act-log-detail lang-en">Together with Technical Advisor (15+ years experience). Soil TDS sampling at 5 points — result: sandy soil with mineral deficiency. Assessment of 915 tree conditions. Harvest projection set: June–July 2026, ±4 rounds.</div>
              <span class="report-link lang-id">📄 Lihat Laporan Kunjungan →</span>
              <span class="report-link lang-en">📄 View Visit Report →</span>
            </div>
            <div class="act-log-meta"><strong>20 Apr 2026</strong>Kunjungan ke-1</div>
          </div>
          <div class="act-log-item">
            <span class="act-log-status s-ongoing lang-id">⟳ Berjalan</span>
            <span class="act-log-status s-ongoing lang-en">⟳ Ongoing</span>
            <div class="act-log-body">
              <div class="act-log-title lang-id">Pengadaan Pupuk Kandang (Prioritas Utama)</div>
              <div class="act-log-title lang-en">Organic Fertilizer Procurement (Top Priority)</div>
              <div class="act-log-detail lang-id">Pupuk kandang menjadi prioritas karena tanah berpasir — kandungan P tinggi dari pupuk organik sangat dibutuhkan untuk meningkatkan mineral tanah sebelum panen.</div>
              <div class="act-log-detail lang-en">Organic fertilizer is a priority due to sandy soil — high P content from organic fertilizer is urgently needed to improve soil minerals before harvest.</div>
            </div>
            <div class="act-log-meta"><strong>Target</strong>Sebelum Jun</div>
          </div>
          <div class="act-log-item">
            <span class="act-log-status s-planned lang-id">◎ Direncanakan</span>
            <span class="act-log-status s-planned lang-en">◎ Planned</span>
            <div class="act-log-body">
              <div class="act-log-title lang-id">Pruning Selektif</div>
              <div class="act-log-title lang-en">Selective Pruning</div>
              <div class="act-log-detail lang-id">Pemangkasan cabang tidak produktif — memfokuskan nutrisi ke cabang berbuah. Alat pruning (kerasi manual/mesin) sedang diadakan.</div>
              <div class="act-log-detail lang-en">Pruning of unproductive branches — focusing nutrients to fruit-bearing branches. Pruning tools (manual/machine shears) being procured.</div>
            </div>
            <div class="act-log-meta"><strong>Mei–Jun</strong>2026</div>
          </div>
          <div class="act-log-item">
            <span class="act-log-status s-planned lang-id">◎ Direncanakan</span>
            <span class="act-log-status s-planned lang-en">◎ Planned</span>
            <div class="act-log-body">
              <div class="act-log-title lang-id">Identifikasi OPT (Hama & Penyakit)</div>
              <div class="act-log-title lang-en">Pest & Disease Identification (OPT)</div>
              <div class="act-log-detail lang-id">Survei menyeluruh hama dan penyakit tanaman — belum dilakukan pada kunjungan pertama. Akan dilaksanakan pada kunjungan lapangan berikutnya bersama Tenaga Ahli.</div>
              <div class="act-log-detail lang-en">Comprehensive pest and disease survey — not yet conducted during the first visit. To be carried out during the next field visit with the Technical Advisor.</div>
            </div>
            <div class="act-log-meta"><strong>Kunjungan</strong>Berikutnya</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="phase-block">
        <div class="phase-block-header">
          <span class="phase-block-icon">☕</span>
          <span class="phase-block-title lang-id">Panen</span>
          <span class="phase-block-title lang-en">Harvest</span>
          <span class="phase-block-period lang-id">Jun – Agt 2026</span>
          <span class="phase-block-period lang-en">Jun – Aug 2026</span>
