        <div class="act-log-list">
          <div class="act-log-item">
            <span class="act-log-status s-upcoming lang-id">↗ Akan Datang</span>
            <span class="act-log-status s-upcoming lang-en">↗ Upcoming</span>
            <div class="act-log-body">
              <div class="act-log-title lang-id">Panen Perdana Post-Wakaf (±4 Ronde)</div>
              <div class="act-log-title lang-en">First Post-Waqf Harvest (±4 Rounds)</div>
              <div class="act-log-detail lang-id">Panen dilakukan bertahap karena kopi tidak masak serentak. Estimasi 4 ronde pemetikan selektif dari Juni hingga Agustus 2026. Hasil akan didokumentasikan per ronde dan dipublikasikan terbuka.</div>
              <div class="act-log-detail lang-en">Harvest is done in stages because coffee does not ripen uniformly. Estimated 4 rounds of selective picking from June to August 2026. Results will be documented per round and published openly.</div>
            </div>
            <div class="act-log-meta"><strong>Est. Jun–Agt</strong>±4 Ronde</div>
          </div>
        </div>
