      <div class="phase-block">
        <div class="phase-block-header">
          <span class="phase-block-icon">🌿</span>
          <span class="phase-block-title lang-id">Post-Panen & Intervensi</span>
          <span class="phase-block-title lang-en">Post-Harvest & Intervention</span>
          <span class="phase-block-period lang-id">Sep – Okt 2026</span>
          <span class="phase-block-period lang-en">Sep – Oct 2026</span>
        </div>
        <div class="act-log-list">
          <div class="act-log-item">
            <span class="act-log-status s-planned lang-id">◎ Direncanakan</span>
            <span class="act-log-status s-planned lang-en">◎ Planned</span>
            <div class="act-log-body">
              <div class="act-log-title lang-id">Pruning Total + Pemulihan Tanah</div>
              <div class="act-log-title lang-en">Full Pruning + Soil Recovery</div>
              <div class="act-log-detail lang-id">Pruning total 30–50 cm dari batang — memaksa pohon berproduksi lebih pada siklus berikutnya. Bersamaan dengan program pemulihan tanah (olah tanah, pupuk organik siklus kedua).</div>
              <div class="act-log-detail lang-en">Full pruning 30–50 cm from the trunk — forcing trees to produce more in the next cycle. Concurrent with soil recovery program (tillage, second-cycle organic fertilizer).</div>
            </div>
            <div class="act-log-meta"><strong>Sep–Okt</strong>2026</div>
          </div>
          <div class="act-log-item">
            <span class="act-log-status s-planned lang-id">◎ Direncanakan</span>
            <span class="act-log-status s-planned lang-en">◎ Planned</span>
            <div class="act-log-body">
              <div class="act-log-title lang-id">Baseline Riset Post-Intervensi</div>
              <div class="act-log-title lang-en">Post-Intervention Research Baseline</div>
              <div class="act-log-detail lang-id">Pengambilan data tanah, kondisi pohon, dan hasil panen pasca-intervensi — membandingkan dengan baseline April 2026. Data ini terbuka untuk peneliti dan akademisi.</div>
              <div class="act-log-detail lang-en">Soil data collection, tree condition, and post-intervention harvest results — comparing with the April 2026 baseline. This data is open to researchers and academics.</div>
            </div>
            <div class="act-log-meta"><strong>Okt–Nov</strong>2026</div>
